  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink38-kilavi">talaimakaṉ maṉaivayiṉ pōkak karutiṉāṉ eṉpatu colliya taṉ tōḻikkup parattai
          colliyatu.</p>
        <p xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>

      <div rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="Aink38">
          <l> amma vāḻi tōḻi makiḻnaṉ</l>
          <l>ṟaṉco luṇarntō raṟiyala ṉeṉṟun</l>
          <l>taṇṭaḷir vauvu mēṉi</l>
          <l>yoṇṭoṭi muṉkai yāmaḻap pirintē.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg xml:lang="en">
          <l> Alas, [my] friend! </l>
          <l> The bringer of delight</l>
          <l> doesn't know that that there were people who overheard his words [OR: he doesn't understand (the love of) women who take his words to heart],</l>
          <l> when he left, [leaving us] to weep–</l>
          <l> [our] forearms with bright bangles, our body</l>
          <l>forever</l>
          <l>catching [the colour of] cool sprouts.</l>


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
  </text>
